                        <interp inst="t18430227-name-724" type="given" value="THOMAS GLOMER"></interp>THOMAS GLOMER MILES</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the service of William Hunter and Sons. I got these four pairs of chair-back screens out, and ordered them to be packed—they are my master's.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was taken out of a crowd of fifteen or sixteen per<lb></lb>sons; I was there five minutes; I was taken more on suspicion, answering the description of the person, than being the person.</p>
